{"title":"解决github fatal: unable to access 'xxxx': Could not resolve host:xxx的问题","date":"2018-01-23T07:38:51.000Z","slug":"解决github-fatal-unable-to-access-xxxx-Could-not-resolve-host-xxx的问题","comments":true,"tags":["Github"],"updated":"2019-05-11T17:11:54.103Z","content":"<p>这两天遇到一个诡异的问题，就是突然git的push和pull用不了了。报如下错误：<br><img src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/img/201801/23152824_lCiD.jpg\" alt=\"报错\" title=\"报错\"></p>\n<p>之后去Google baidu了一波，找到一个靠谱的解决方案：</p>\n<p>首先ping 代码仓库地址：<br> <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ping gitlab.alibaba-inc.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>如果报错：</p>\n<div class=\"article-img\"><p><img src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/img/201801/23153234_UgIR.jpg\" alt=\"ping\" title=\"ping\" data-zoomable></p></div>\n<p>那找一台能ping的通的机器，看一下ping通后的ip地址是多少：<br><img src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/img/201801/23153527_K72O.png\" alt=\"找到ip地址\" title=\"找到ip地址\"></p>\n<p>最后一步就是把ip地址和代码仓库地址加入本机hosts：<br><img src=\"https://static.oschina.net/uploads/img/201801/23153731_PsR2.jpg\" alt=\"加入hosts文件\" title=\"加入hosts文件\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"设计模式之单例模式","slug":"设计模式之单例模式"},"next":{"title":"dubbo异常: Failed to invoke the method getFormulaZtree in the service 异常解决方案","slug":"dubbo异常-Failed-to-invoke-the-method-getFormulaZtree-in-the-service-异常解决方案"},"link":"http://wooo.io/post/解决github-fatal-unable-to-access-xxxx-Could-not-resolve-host-xxx的问题/"}